---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Privacy Policy";
const description = "SnapFitLabs Privacy Policy";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-600 font-light">At SnapFitLabs, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your data and your rights regarding your personal information.</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">1. Data Collection</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 font-light">We do not collect any personal data from our users. Our app does not require you to provide any personal information, and we do not track your usage or behavior.</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">2. Third-Party Data Sharing</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 font-light">Since we do not collect any personal data, we do not share any data with third parties. We do not use any analytics tools, advertising networks, or third-party SDKs that would require data sharing.</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">3. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 font-light">As we do not collect any personal data, there is no data to retain or delete. Your privacy is ensured by our policy of not collecting any data in the first place.</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">4. User Consent and Data Deletion Requests</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 font-light">Since we do not collect any personal data, there is no need for you to revoke consent or request data deletion. Your privacy is protected by our commitment to not collecting any data.</p>
</Layout>

<style>
  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', 'Poppins', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  }

  h1, h2 {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  p {
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  a {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .shadow-lg {
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), -8px -8px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .rounded-lg {
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
</style>
